729633f-a.folder: Seaview Avenue & Quincy Avenue, Staten Island, NY
729633f-a.text:
Seaview Avenue, north from Quincy Avenue, showing the thoroughfare under construction. Note the steel beams (near detour sign) for the erection of the bridge over New Creek.

P. L. Sperr
